			<div id="post_wrapper" class="skinny_wrapper">
				<div class="post">
					<h2>Weather Application Design</h2>				
					<hr>
					<img src="images/Weather_1.gif" alt="images">
					<div class="sub_post">
						<h4>Overview</h4>
						<p>
							The main purpose of the project is to develop unique visual design concepts through
							exploring and expressing the weather mobile application. The focus was to aesthetically 
							redesign an existing product  without adding or removing features or modifying workflows.
						</p>
						<h4>Problem</h4>
						<p>
							The original Weather application looks simple, organized, and beautiful. However,
							most of the weather applications use similar styles. 
						</p>
						<h4>Solution</h4>
						<p>
							Maximize the simplicity plus aesthetical design. 
						</p>
						<h4>Moodboard</h4>
